					<p>My goal is to work on <i>Anacreon</i> in two-week sprints. Each sprint will result in a new release, although I might release additional versions in case of severe bugs.</p>
					<p>For example, the Alpha 3 sprint begins on Monday 21 January 2013 and ends with a release on Friday 1 Feburary 2013. (The Alpha 2 sprint is not exactly 2 weeks because of the Holidays.)</p>
